4 sūryaḥ mama dakṣiṇe skandhe abhighātayati sma, 5 yaḥ, asmāt pūrva eva prakāśamānaḥ, samagram paścimam diśam 6 śyāmalasya śuklavarṇe parivartayati sma;
7 aham ca svayaṃ chāyāyāḥ atiprakāśena 8 jvālām iva darśayāmi sma; tataś ca tathāvidhena lakṣaṇena 9 gacchan anekāḥ chāyāḥ mama dṛṣṭipathe āgacchan.

