query.result:
**English:**
10 This was the cause that gave them the beginning 11 to speak of me; and they began 12 to say: "That one does not seem a fictitious body";
13 then toward me, as much as they could advance, 14 some drew near, always with caution 15 not to come out where they would not be burned.
